### Pillow -- PIL -- pip install pillow

from PIL import Image

computer = Image.open('example.jpg')

computer

computer.size

(1993, 1257)

computer.resize((100,100))

computer

computer.rotate(90)

halfway = 1993/2

x = halfway - 200
w = halfway + 200

y = 800
h = 1257

new = computer.crop((x,y,w,h))

computer = computer.paste(new, (0,0))

computer

red

red

red
